author: jonl
msg: Removed TODO for custom labels in radio option sets since they are already supported via resource string loading.

author: jonl
msg: Simplified choices so they just have a single is/setNullValid() property.  When
null is valid, the <name>.null string resource is loaded and used.  When null is
not valid and the selection is null, <name>.null is loaded and used to display
something like "Choose One", since a null selection is not valid.

author: jonl
msg: Fixed bug where component tree would fail if model threw an exception.  Instead, the exception message is shown as the model value.
